Walmart is now reserving an hour each day for pickup orders for shoppers most at risk for the coronavirus.
First responders also are included in Walmart's new curbside pickup hour.
Several stores including Walmart also have added senior shopping hours.
Walmart's weekly hour-long senior shopping event is every Tuesday for customers 60 and older and starts one hour before the retailer's 5,000-plus U.S. stores open.
